#: ../../S/shebang.rst:5
msgid "shebang"
msgstr "shebang"

#: ../../S/shebang.rst:7
msgid "/sh\\@·bang/, n\\."
msgstr "/sh\\@·bang/, 名詞"

#: ../../S/shebang.rst:9
msgid ""
"[possibly a portmanteau of \"sharp bang\"] The character sequence \"#!\" "
"that frequently begins executable shell scripts under Unix. Probably derived"
" from \"shell bang\" under the influence of American slang \"the whole "
"shebang\" (everything, the works)."
msgstr ""
"[おそらく「sharp bang」のかばん語] Unixで実行可能なシェルスクリプトの先頭によく置かれる文字列「#!」。おそらく、米国の俗語「the "
"whole shebang(何もかも、一切合切)」の影響のもとで「shell bang」から派生した。"
